data.Name: Thundercats
data.Bio: Thundercats is a moniker of the hip-hop group Mighty Jukebox from Iceland. This group consists of Fonetik Simbol (producer) and S. Creeezy (rapper). It may also be an incorrect artist tag for a soundtrack by various artists. If so, do last.fm and yourself a favour. Fix your tags by putting the actual artist name in the artist field. Read more on Last.fm
